⌃ = control
⌥ = option
⇧ = shift 

File Navigation
---------------
go to file:            ⌘ T
go to symbol:        ⇧ ⌘ T 
go to line:            ⌘ L
ﬁnd in file:           ⌘ F  
ﬁnd in project:      ⇧ ⌘ F
reveal in project:   ⌃ ⌘ R
set bookmark:          ⌘ F2
cycle bookmarks:         F2

HTML
----
wrap block in tag:   ⌃ ⇧ W
insert html tag:     ⌃ ⇧ ,
insert ruby code:    ⌃ ⇧ .
insert closing tag:  ⌥ ⌘ .

Editing
-------
code completion:          esc
fold / unfold:            F1
comment selection:      ⌘ /
indent selection left:  ⌘ [
indent selection right: ⌘ ]
column selection:       ⌥ (drag)

Ruby/Rails tab triggers
-----------------------
class: cla (tab)
method: def (tab)
module: mod (tab)
has_many: hm (tab)
belongs_to: bt (tab)
lambda: lam (tab)</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
